WEBVTT

00:00:00.073 --> 00:00:01.540
You never give it any thought,

00:00:01.564 --> 00:00:03.845
and there are billions of them out there,

00:00:03.869 --> 00:00:07.416
but the amount of design
and passion and creativity

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:12.296
that goes into this
little disc is remarkable.

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:13.553
[Small thing.]

00:00:13.577 --> 00:00:15.449
[Big idea.]

00:00:18.033 --> 00:00:22.350
The coffee cup lid
is a lid for your coffee cup.

00:00:22.374 --> 00:00:23.711
It snaps on.

00:00:23.735 --> 00:00:24.958
It has an opening.

00:00:24.982 --> 00:00:28.479
You've got lids with a little
latch that opens and closes.

00:00:28.503 --> 00:00:31.110
You've got ones that
are in creative shapes.